1
00:00:40,920 --> 00:00:41,719
Jiao Jing, don't move.

2
00:00:41,719 --> 00:00:42,960
Put the knife down.

3
00:00:42,960 --> 00:00:44,200
What I can't have,

4
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:46,039
you can't have either.

5
00:00:48,079 --> 00:00:48,880
Hold on.

6
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:49,560
Yihai!

7
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,759
Yihai, hold on!

8
00:01:00,439 --> 00:01:01,079
Brother Hai.

9
00:01:01,439 --> 00:01:03,320
The guy who hurt Huilian, we got him.

10
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:05,200
He can really take a beating.

11
00:01:08,439 --> 00:01:09,400
Dahai...

12
00:01:10,519 --> 00:01:11,959
Wake up soon.

13
00:01:12,439 --> 00:01:13,959
Everyone's waiting for you.

14
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:17,640
Dahai, how long are you gonna sleep?

15
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:22,719
Don't worry, I'm here.

16
00:01:28,519 --> 00:01:29,400
Where are you wiping?

17
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:30,560
You...

18
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,640
Is it any of your business?

19
00:01:32,239 --> 00:01:33,079
Hand it over.

20
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:34,959
Give it to me.

21
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:36,519
Give it!

22
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,560
You're getting physical now?

23
00:01:39,319 --> 00:01:40,239
You wanna fight?

24
00:01:40,239 --> 00:01:41,359
I'd have kicked your ass long ago!

25
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,120
Fine, bring it on!

26
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,280
Stop!

27
00:01:47,519 --> 00:01:48,640
I'm counting to three.

28
00:01:48,959 --> 00:01:49,840
Both of you, let go!

29
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,400
Alright, one.

30
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:52,439
Two.

31
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:53,400
Three.

32
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:57,280
How can you fight so dirty, bitch?

33
00:01:57,799 --> 00:01:58,840
You're no better.

34
00:01:58,840 --> 00:01:59,719
You let go!

35
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:00,799
Are you letting go or not?

36
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:01,480
You let go first.

37
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:11,840
Lili.

38
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,319
Yihai, you're awake!

39
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,280
Ge Bing.

40
00:02:20,719 --> 00:02:21,599
How long was I out?

41
00:02:21,759 --> 00:02:23,240
You've been out for days.

42
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:33,199
How's Dali doing?

43
00:02:35,199 --> 00:02:36,879
Liu Tianqi has been arrested.

44
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,120
The statement's all done.

45
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,039
See?

46
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:41,960
I told you I had nothing to do with Long Xiao.

47
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,479
I believe you.

48
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:46,240
Thank you.

49
00:02:46,599 --> 00:02:47,319
For donating blood.

50
00:02:47,719 --> 00:02:48,400
For saving my life.

51
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,400
Actually,

52
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,560
don't thank me.

53
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:54,159
Our blood types don't match.

54
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,439
Then aren't you my...

55
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,039
I'm not your what?

56
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:00,120
Nothing, nothing.

57
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,800
What are you gonna do next?

58
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,280
I have to make sure

59
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:07,360
my dad won't work with Giant Wood Group.

60
00:03:07,919 --> 00:03:09,360
And if that doesn't work out?

61
00:03:09,759 --> 00:03:10,680
If it doesn't,

62
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:11,800
then I'll go abroad.

63
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:14,919
I don't wanna see the factory ruined by him.

64
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,240
How about

65
00:03:17,639 --> 00:03:18,639
you come abroad with me?

66
00:03:20,879 --> 00:03:23,000
I-I don't wanna be a burden.

67
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,960
You can be my interpreter.

68
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,039
Silly.

69
00:03:28,439 --> 00:03:29,319
Going abroad

70
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:31,400
isn't something you can just do whenever.

71
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:42,759
Here, this is for you.

72
00:03:43,719 --> 00:03:45,800
Found it on the kidnappers.

73
00:03:50,159 --> 00:03:51,080
You're awake too.

74
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:52,360
I'll head back now.

75
00:03:52,479 --> 00:03:53,479
Get well soon.

76
00:04:01,759 --> 00:04:02,360
Ge Bing.

77
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:05,520
Heh.

78
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:16,079
Not bad, Brother Hai.

79
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,240
Another one.

80
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,839
Wei Wei.

81
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:22,360
Little brat.

82
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,360
What are you doing here?

83
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,800
Applying medicine.

84
00:04:29,199 --> 00:04:30,199
I heard everything.

85
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,240
You turned her down

86
00:04:34,639 --> 00:04:35,879
because of Lili, right?

87
00:04:39,839 --> 00:04:41,040
Let me ask you something.

88
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:43,040
Say a guy

89
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:45,839
time-travels into his father's body,

90
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:47,480
but he never meets his mom.

91
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:49,000
Could those two

92
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,560
ever end up giving birth to him?

93
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,480
No way.

94
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:58,480
That's what I thought.

95
00:04:59,639 --> 00:05:01,360
So I gotta be with Lili.

96
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,279
With Lili...

97
00:05:03,279 --> 00:05:03,759
With...

98
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:07,120
You wanna go after Lili!

99
00:05:07,439 --> 00:05:08,040
You wanna go after Lili!

100
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:08,480
Hurry up then.

101
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,639
Just go for her.

102
00:05:11,439 --> 00:05:14,319
Quit hemming and hawing about it.

103
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:16,399
I saw her having dinner with another guy.

104
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:18,120
Who? How old was he?

105
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,160
I didn't get a good look.

106
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,560
But it was at the Seafood House.

107
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:23,079
Then he's gotta be a rich guy.

108
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,800
Totally unnecessary.

109
00:05:27,319 --> 00:05:28,120
Brother Hai, you're awake.

110
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,720
That Liu Tianqi punk got locked up.

111
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,279
Don't worry.

112
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:31,639
Sooner or later he'll rat out Long Xiao.

113
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,040
Good.

114
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,639
Once Long Xiao goes down,

115
00:05:34,959 --> 00:05:36,000
we'll all be in the clear.

116
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:40,560
Then shouldn't we take care of our own business?

117
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,480
What business?

118
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:45,279
You better get the red envelopes ready.

119
00:05:45,879 --> 00:05:46,800
Red envelopes?

120
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,000
Brother Hai, come on, tell me.

121
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:50,560
Who is it?

122
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,600
Who do you think?

123
00:05:51,879 --> 00:05:52,639
Lili.

124
00:05:52,639 --> 00:05:53,480
Lili?

125
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,560
Brother, you're making your move?

126
00:05:54,759 --> 00:05:56,079
Keep your voice down.

127
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:56,959
We're in a hospital.

128
00:05:58,319 --> 00:05:59,079
So what's your plan?

129
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:00,959
That's why I was thinking,

130
00:06:00,959 --> 00:06:02,720
you two should help me figure it out.

131
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,279
What's there to figure out?

132
00:06:04,279 --> 00:06:05,839
Just use your old playbook

133
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:06,959
all over again.

134
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:08,680
What old playbook?

135
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,680
A little movie,

136
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:10,600
you watch it together,

137
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,560
her little hand,

138
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,240
you grab it,

139
00:06:13,399 --> 00:06:14,439
and boom, you're in.

140
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,959
No way.

141
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:18,160
Going to a movie is too lame.

142
00:06:18,519 --> 00:06:20,959
Isn't that how you went after Huilian?

143
00:06:20,959 --> 00:06:22,680
Now suddenly it's too lame for you?

144
00:06:31,759 --> 00:06:33,079
This should be enough, right?

145
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:34,959
Alright.

146
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:40,600
Holy crap.

147
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:42,720
Qian Huilian.

148
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,600
You're lurking around like a ghost all day.

149
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,480
What's the matter?

150
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,639
Haunting me?

151
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:48,879
Are you out of your mind?

152
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:50,720
When have I ever come here for you?

153
00:06:51,439 --> 00:06:52,240
Let's talk.

154
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,959
Talk about what? I gotta get to the hospital.

155
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,480
Hurry up.

156
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,279
Spit it out.

157
00:07:04,399 --> 00:07:05,600
This sixty thousand yuan,

158
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,360
you take it.

159
00:07:08,519 --> 00:07:10,079
Hey, Qian Huilian, what's that supposed to mean?

160
00:07:10,879 --> 00:07:11,800
You think this sixty thousand

161
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,480
is gonna make me give up Brother Hai?

162
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:15,399
Stop making such a fuss all the time.

163
00:07:15,959 --> 00:07:17,959
This is insurance I bought without telling him.

164
00:07:17,959 --> 00:07:19,319
Remember to renew it for him later.

165
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,560
Look at you showing off.

166
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,279
Don't tell him.

167
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,240
I'm leaving.

168
00:07:25,639 --> 00:07:26,319
Hold on.

169
00:07:28,079 --> 00:07:29,079
Qian Huilian.

170
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:30,439
What are you getting at?

171
00:07:30,759 --> 00:07:31,399
Do you have any idea

172
00:07:31,399 --> 00:07:32,839
how hard Brother Hai worked

173
00:07:32,839 --> 00:07:34,040
to pay back this sixty thousand?

174
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:36,120
Why are you giving it back to him now?

175
00:07:38,759 --> 00:07:39,560
Qiao Lili.

176
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:42,120
You don't really think

177
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,240
Zhu Yihai owes me money, do you?

178
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,199
What else?

179
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,879
Didn't you open this pool hall for him?

180
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,079
What's between us

181
00:07:50,079 --> 00:07:52,079
can't be settled that easily.

182
00:07:52,839 --> 00:07:54,399
That sixty thousand debt

183
00:07:54,399 --> 00:07:55,759
was just an excuse.

184
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:56,360
Get it?

185
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,079
Hey, Qian Huilian,

186
00:07:58,079 --> 00:08:00,079
What's with all this back and forth?

187
00:08:00,399 --> 00:08:01,920
Brother Hai's doing fine with me looking after him.

188
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:02,720
You can rest easy.

189
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,600
Can't you tell good advice from bad?

190
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,600
Show some sense, would you?

191
00:08:07,319 --> 00:08:09,040
Take this and keep it safe.

192
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,000
And don't say a word.

193
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,240
With all the fighting going on,

194
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,600
it'll come in handy sooner or later.

195
00:08:14,279 --> 00:08:14,879
I'm off.

196
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,399
I was just saying...

197
00:08:43,519 --> 00:08:44,159
Don't move!

198
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:46,799
What is your business here?

199
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:48,720
I'm with the Imperial Army.

200
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,039
You don't look like Imperial Army.

201
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:52,120
You must be a Collaborator Interpreter.

202
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:53,960
Pretty girl.

203
00:08:56,679 --> 00:08:57,399
You're here.

204
00:08:57,399 --> 00:08:58,159
Yeah.

205
00:08:58,840 --> 00:08:59,559
This is for you.

206
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,559
How thoughtful.

207
00:09:02,559 --> 00:09:04,480
Why'd you ask me to Dongxing Factory?

208
00:09:04,679 --> 00:09:05,799
All mysterious like this.

209
00:09:06,279 --> 00:09:08,200
Just out of the hospital and showing off?

210
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,679
I was just thinking,

211
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:11,919
they're playing my favorite movie here.

212
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:15,000
I figured I had to watch it with you.

213
00:09:16,799 --> 00:09:17,639
What movie?

214
00:09:18,279 --> 00:09:19,000
Come on, hurry up.

215
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,879
Or we'll miss the opening.

216
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,080
So weird and secretive.

217
00:09:30,759 --> 00:09:32,399
Your leather jacket looks great today.

218
00:09:33,759 --> 00:09:35,519
You like this style, right?

219
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:36,960
Not really.

220
00:09:52,679 --> 00:09:53,480
Dahai

221
00:09:55,039 --> 00:09:56,759
Why'd you ask me to a movie today?

222
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:59,840
Well, it's because Dali and the others

223
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:00,840
keep calling you

224
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,879
"Sis, Sis" all the time.

225
00:10:03,399 --> 00:10:04,440
So I was thinking...

226
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,440
Thinking what?

227
00:10:07,919 --> 00:10:09,360
Look at you, you're impossible.

228
00:10:16,519 --> 00:10:18,200
I'll let you in on a secret.

229
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:22,200
I've got a surprise for you.

230
00:10:24,399 --> 00:10:25,200
What's wrong?

231
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:26,360
Nothing.

232
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:29,360
Have some seeds

233
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:31,279
while you watch.

234
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:32,279
Mm-hmm.

235
00:10:33,559 --> 00:10:34,679
A surprise.

236
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:37,000
What's the surprise?

237
00:10:37,639 --> 00:10:39,000
If it's really that, then I...

238
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,440
On behalf of my dad...

239
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:03,360
This is nice.

240
00:11:15,679 --> 00:11:17,720
That's so weird.

241
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:22,279
Did your leg cramp up or something?

242
00:11:26,399 --> 00:11:28,039
Isn't that Qiao Lili?

243
00:11:28,919 --> 00:11:29,919
You know her?

244
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:31,799
No. Ignore him, he's a nutjob.

245
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,480
Excuse me

246
00:12:02,279 --> 00:12:03,279
Is Zhu Yihai here?

247
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:04,840
No, he's not.

248
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:07,080
Who are you?

249
00:12:11,799 --> 00:12:12,360
Oh my

250
00:12:12,679 --> 00:12:14,000
Long time no see.

251
00:12:17,559 --> 00:12:18,480
Jiao Jing.

252
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,000
You've got the nerve to show up?

253
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:21,919
Cut the crap.

254
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,039
Where's Zhu Yihai?

255
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:24,399
It's getting late.

256
00:12:24,639 --> 00:12:25,759
You should head home.

257
00:12:26,039 --> 00:12:27,279
Whatever happens with Zhu Yihai

258
00:12:27,279 --> 00:12:29,399
has nothing to do with you anymore.

259
00:12:30,639 --> 00:12:32,039
I don't mean anything by it.

260
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:34,360
I just came to warn him.

261
00:12:35,039 --> 00:12:36,320
Long Xiao's about to make his move.

